options.content:
# Special thanks
## Licenses
MaaS is on top of softwares of the following opensource licenses: 
Apache 2.0, Apache License 2.0, Apache Software License, Apache-2.0, Apache-2.0 OR BSD-3-Clause, Apache-2.0 license, BSD, BSD 3-Clause, BSD License, BSD-2-Clause, BSD-3-Clause, Dual License, HPND, ISC, LGPL, LGPL-2.1-or-later, MIT, MIT License, MPL-2.0, PSFL, Python Software Foundation License
## Credits
MaaS depends on the work of many other developers. Time to say a great thank you for all your work in the open source ecosystem !
